<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. <span class="c2">(فَلَسْتُ أَرَى إِلا الَّذِي فَلَق النَّوَى<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>هُوَ الْوَاحِدُ الْمُعْطِي كَثِيرُ الْمَوَاهِبِ)<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(وَمُعْتَصَمُ الْمكْرُوبِ فِي كُلِّ غَمْرَةٍ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَمُنْتَجَعُ الْغُفْرَانِ مِنْ كُلِّ هَائِبِ)<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(مُجِيبُ دُعَا الْمُضْطَّرِ عِنْدَ دُعَائِهِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَمُنْقِذُهُ مِنْ مُعْضِلاتِ النَّوَائِبِ)<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(مُعِيدُ الْوَرَى فِي زَجْرَةٍ بَعْدَ مَوْتِهِمْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>لِفَصْلِ حُقُوقٍ بَيْنَهُمْ وَمَطَالِبِ)<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>فَفِي ذَلِكَ الْيَوْمِ الْعَصِيبِ تَرَى الْوَرَى<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>سُكَارَى وَلا سُكْرٌ بِهِمْ مِنْ مَشَارِبِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>حُفَاةً عُرَاةً خَاشِعِينَ لِرَبِّهِمْ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَيَا وَيْحَ ذِي ظُلْمٍ رَهِينَ الْمَطَالِبِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>فَيَأْتُوا لِنُوحٍ وَالْخَلِيلِ وَآدَمٍ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَمُوسَى وَعِيسَى عِنْدَ تِلْكَ الْمَتَاعِبِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>لَعَلَّهُمُ أَنْ يَشْفَعُوا عِنْدَ رَبِّهِمْ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>لَتَخْلِيصِهِمْ مِنْ مُعْضِلاتِ الْمَصَاعِبِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فَمَا كَانَ يُغْنِي عَنْهُمُوا عِنْدَ هَذِهِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>نَبِيٌّ وَلَمْ يُظْفِرْهُمُ بِالْمَآرِبِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>هنَاكَ رَسُولُ اللهِ يَأْتِي لِرَبِّهِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>لِيَشْفَعْ لِتَخْلِيصِ الْوَرَى مِنْ مَتَاعِبِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>